title: Didnt recieved the Party poro icon yet
body:
Thats all. Riot gave me kayle's skin like 7 days ago but not the icon yet. :C
Anyone still like me?

replies.body: Gifts are being sent out still and will take some more time, per our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  There are a lot of accounts to cover, so hang tight.  The goodies will come!
Riot had to extend the time it's going to take to give out the gifts until September 30th.
